title: Syncing account to see if it fixes my forum issue
body:
With this post I hope to sync my account.

I should be level higher level and I read on the boards as less.

This in reference to the "My level is not updating on the boards" post.

Please feel free to ignore this post. Thanks

replies.body: Yup, it looks like your account has sync'd up with the boards.  Happy posting!
